					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Case 1 sounds correct. But technically, you don't even need an IRQ for a top status bar, as you can arrange for a sprite 0 hit as <em>Super Mario Bros.</em> does it.<br /><br />Case 2 could be simplified by having the IRQ handler index into an array. The array in the IRQ handler of <em>The Curse of Possum Hollow</em> holds up to eight X positions, bank numbers, and strip heights.</div>

